high_descs: turn around and go to the microwave in the right-hand corner of the room
open the microwave, take the egg from the left-side, and close the microwave door
turn left, and cross the room to the counter to the sink
place the egg in the sink, rinse the contents of the sink, and then take the egg again
move slightly right along the counter, stopping in front of the yellow apple
place the egg on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg in front of the yellow apple

high_descs: Turn left to face the island then turn left facing the toaster and a right to go towards the microwave on the counter.
Open the microwave and take the egg on the left and shut the door.
Turn left and walk towards the stove with the egg. Go straight then a slight left so you are facing the counter by the sink. Walk towards the counter.
Place the egg in the sink and turn on the water. Turn the water off and take the egg back out.
Turn right with the egg and then left towards the counter next to the sink.
Place the egg on the counter in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Clean an egg from the microwave to place it on the counter.

high_descs: turn around and walk to the kitchen counter at the end of the room on your right, then turn to face the microwave there
grab an egg out of the microwave, the egg on the left specifically
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the end of the room again
place the egg inside of the sink there, rinse it off, then pick it back up
move to the right a bit, and face the kitchen counter again
place the egg down on the kitchen counter in front of you
anns.task_desc: place a rinsed off egg on the kitchen counter right of the sink
